☞『 save|share|like|comment|tag 』

Starting today, I will be posting more swipe workouts for you guys to follow and get little more details on each exercise. Of course daily reel workout is still happening + swipe workouts!
•
Wearing @gymshark @gymsharktrain
☞ White camo logo stringer (sm)
☞ 5” black arrival short (sm)
☞ Link in bio
•
FULL WORKOUT SWIPE LEFT:
1. Alt. DB Curl: 4 x 12-15
2. Iso Curl: 4 x 12-15
3. Spider Hammer: 4 x 12-15
4. EZ Bar Curl: 4 x 12-15
5. Underhand Curl: 4 x 12-15

📝: Keep your movements controlled and steady with nice tempo. If you’re swinging your body too much, go lighter. Don’t go too heavy, squeeze at top and feel the burn. Take a 30-45 sec breather in between sets.
